These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, gardening, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | singing | gardening | magic-tricks   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
3 different pets are kept: hamster, dog, rabbit
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the dog is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| Pet   | dog | hamster | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
City: hannover, san-francisco, london
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| City       | hannover     | san-francisco | london |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
City: berlin, paris, edinburgh
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| City    | edinburgh    | paris     | berlin |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
City: marseilles, venice, berlin
1. the person traveling to venice is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| City   | berlin        | marseilles | venice    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, ebony, blue
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who likes blue is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Color        | blue | grey      | ebony  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia, azalea
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Flower           | amaryllis | azalea | dahlia |

