.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite    | tea    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | helicopter | airplane |

