.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, dunhill, davidoff
1. the fan of trance is the prince-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Cigar   | davidoff    | prince | dunhill |

