.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, golf, volleyball
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, nigerian
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Sport   | volleyball    | basketball     | golf   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | nigerian |

