3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the wooden house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| House   | cape-cod    | wooden | craftsman |
| Pet   | hedgehog | chinchilla     | fish        |

