2. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Pet      | bird  | frog | guinea-pig  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

