.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lemon, peach
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the far left##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the far right##1
3. the american is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Food           | lemon | peach | garlic |
| Nationality   | turkish  | american      | colombian |

