.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, car
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Transport    | jet-ski | car   | quad-bike        |
| Sport   | skiing    | climbing | weightlifting |

