.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, skateboarding, sailing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, pop
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the fan of pop##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Sport         | surfing | skateboarding | sailing |
| Music-Genre   | country | pop     | house  |

