.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, puzzles
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Hobby    | puzzles | fishing       | traveling  |
| Sport   | soccer  | snowboarding | cycling |

 